metadata.name: Flourish
metadata.description:
Flourish, in the literal sense of the word, is about life returning after the winter, organisms coming back to life in spring, my favourite time. 

In a wider sense this is about an artist returning to the scene after hibernation of self doubt and second guessing, something many can identify with.

Flourish invites you to witness the rebirth of creativity, femininity and life, slowly taking graspa dn breaking through the cold, stone-like past.
